{"tid":1062293,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Model Y來了！ 7座豪華SUV，比Model 3更大、更貴","createTime":"2019-03-15T04:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T06:12:28.000Z","uid":1369,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"31ed22b0e81ccf24ade9053d374f2b9b905244c9","tid":1062293,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"馬斯克宣布，特斯拉（TSLA.O）Model Y標準版售價為3.9萬美元/輛，長里程版本的車型價格定在4.7萬美元，MODEL Y標準版將於2021年上市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSRiDON.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSRiDON.png&h=95c2486e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於今日發布的Model Y，馬斯克顯然是胸有成竹。此前在特斯拉的年度股東大會上，馬斯克曾將 Model Y 描述為「something super special.（非常特別的東西）」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYzcJfw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYzcJfw.png&h=a97d0e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且深諳市場消費心態的馬斯克，更是時不時在社交媒體上透露出Model Y的參數信息：3月3號其發推文稱，Model Y是一款運動型多用途汽車（SUV），比Model 3的體積大10%左右，所以成本要高10%左右，且同樣的電池續航里程相對略短。消息一出，立即激起市場對於特斯拉新款SUV莫大的興趣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rv48gAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frv48gAM.png&h=f4ff1024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克甚至預言稱，Model Y 的全球銷量將到達 50 萬~100 萬輛/年。跨過年銷量 100 萬輛的大關，成為真正的「主流」，這款產品對於特斯拉的重要性不言而喻。這也是馬斯克關於電動汽車普及第三階段的重要產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bohxJfR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbohxJfR.png&h=b74eca95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WASauVR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWASauVR.png&h=d66ad62a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d28acdf73f67701be3da0f52264dd6121acced8","tid":1062293,"uid":200247,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:21:32.000Z","msg":"平係好平，但可唔可以唔好好似iPhone一樣出極都係嗰個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aa4130c14ae6e4481433103c0f